title: [Mairiseth Telearat, Cliffwalk]
description: Soft, silken cushions are scattered across the well-tended grass of the expansive lawn, the circular pillows surrounding the low-set resaeun tables resting across the verdant cliffside park.  Canopied booths frame the entryways of the garden-topped limestone buildings, the colorful stalls decorated in a melange of leafy florals.
